\par }{\~
\par }{\f1\fs20\cf11 You would need to add this into the statement.}{
\par \~
\par }{\cs15\b\f1\fs20\cf6 Colour[i]=xmlObj.childNodes[i].childNodes(4).firstChild.text;}{\f1\fs20\cf11 
\par }{\cs15\b\f1\fs20\cf6 Size[i]=xmlObj.childNodes[i].childNodes(5).firstChild.text;}{\f1\fs20\cf11 
